Tatanam do reng dakal a species king tropics antimong '''orchid trees''', partikular king [[pangulu]]ng [[India]], [[Vietnam]] ampong [[mauli]]-[[aslagan]]g [[Maldang Republika ning Tsina|Tsina]]. King [[Estados Unidos]], tutubu la reng pun dutung king [[Hawaii]], king bebe dayatmalat ning [[California]], [[Texas]], [[Louisiana]], ampong [[Florida]]. Ing ''[[Bauhinia blakeana|Bauhinia × blakeana]]'' ing sampagang sagisag (''floral emblem'') ning [[Hong Kong]]&ndash;metung a midisenyung sampagang ''orchid tree'' king [[flag of Hong Kong|bandera ning Hong Kong]], at ing  [[Hong Kong Airlines]], gagamitan ne ing 'Bauhinia' antimong radio callsign king air traffic communication.

